Question.Subject: Why does youtube look different in Internet Explorer to how it looks in Firefox?
Question.Content:
For some reason, youtube looks like this in Explorer: http://s925.photobucket.com/albums/ad93/thisisme272/Youtube/
and it looks like this in Firefox: http://s925.photobucket.com/albums/ad93/thisisme272/Youtube/Youtube%20in%20Firefox/?action=view&current=CapturefromFirefox.jpg
Question.ChosenAnswer: Youtube just updated their website layout. The updated look is on the Explorer, and it will probably be the same in Firefox after some time.

Answer.Content: Youtube just updated their website layout. The updated look is on the Explorer, and it will probably be the same in Firefox after some time.
